Text: "Isn't the capital. People seldom to hear about this place. No one predicted\
  \ it will be famous one day. Maybe in other countries they have same story. About\
  \ an island that not well know but actually have a very great potential inside.\n\
  It's beyond every people's thought now Madeira is more famous than Lisbon / Lisboa.\
  \ Thanks to the great supernova football player Cristiano Ronaldo, now everyone\
  \ know Madeira well and very amazed to the beautiful of this island. It's a very\
  \ amazing island, the coast so wonderful, the Cathedral so magnificent, wine cellar\
  \ so fine, local food so tasty, too much amazing potential until i can't point which\
  \ one is the best. \nIf you want to know more, come and explorer by yourself the\
  \ wonderful of Madeira, the hidden paradise. You will amazed to God creation more\
  \ after you visit this wonderful island. Go Madeira, go CR7 \U0001F609"
